DISTINCTION — DISCOVERED vs INVENTED

512 (constraint set): DISCOVERED — non-ownable.
  Documentation: CC BY 4.0.

CVS (witness architecture): INVENTED — ownable.
  Architecture: Apache 2.0.

This distinction is intentional and architecturally
significant. The constraint set that physics forces into
existence cannot be owned. The engineering solution built
to witness it can be.

